SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16
17
in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 8000 of Title 36, unless there
17
18
is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18
19
As used in this act:
19
20
1. “Health benefit plan” means a health benefit plan as defined
20
21
pursuant to Section 6060.4 of Title 36 of the Oklahoma Statutes; and
21
22
2. “Mandate” means any requirement proposed in legislation or
22
23
regulation that obligates a health benefit plan to:
23
24
